article.headline: Cole has 22, Oakland takes down Toledo 85-52
article.description: — D.Q. Cole had 22 points in Oakland's 85-52 win over Toledo on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Cole has 22, Oakland takes down Toledo 85-52
article.story: TOLEDO, Ohio -- — D.Q. Cole had 22 points in Oakland's 85-52 win over Toledo on Saturday night. Cole also contributed five rebounds for the Golden Grizzlies (2-4). Allen David Mukeba Jr. scored 17 points while shooting 8 of 15 from the field and added six rebounds. Tuburu Niavalurua had 16 points and shot 7 of 10 from the field and 2 of 5 from the free-throw line. Sonny Wilson led the Rockets (5-3) in scoring, finishing with 13 points. Javan Simmons added 10 points and eight rebounds for Toledo. Sam Lewis finished with 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
